    "id": 4,
    "title": "RetentionPolicy",
    "points": [
      "MQTT Retention Period determines how long a message is stored on the broker",
      "Default retention period is 2 hours"
    ],
    "script": "In MQTT, the Retention Period specifies for how long messages are kept by the broker. This can be adjusted to suit the needs of the application."
  },
